| First principle | Implementation |
|-----------------|----------------|
| **Visibility** | Status bar chip `⊙ 2/20 · Refactor demo…` (full + compact TUI) |
| **Feedback** | Flash badges: `↻ goal continuing` / `✓ goal complete` / `⏸ goal paused` |
| **No noise** | Synthetic continuations hidden from transcript (`↻ Continuing toward standing goal…`) |
| **Immediate action** | `/goal set` + `/goal resume` dispatch kickoff when idle (was stuck in queue) |
