### Gateway status ordering (code-is-law note)

Hermes defers goal judge notices via `register_post_delivery_callback`. EdgeCrab runs `goal_evaluate_after_turn` **after** `dispatch_streaming_arc` returns (post-delivery). Status ordering is already correct — no extra deferral needed.

